                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17510557" author="emilles" created="Tue, 22 Mar 2022 15:13:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If &lt;tt&gt;GroovyObject&lt;/tt&gt; could be added to classes in an earlier phase, there are a number of checks that could be removed from &lt;tt&gt;StaticTypeCheckingVisitor&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;StaticTypeCheckingSupport&lt;/tt&gt;, and &lt;tt&gt;AsmClassGenerator&lt;/tt&gt;.  Search for &lt;tt&gt;ClassNode#getCompileUnit&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;ClassNode#isDerivedFromGroovyObject&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;StaticTypeCheckingSupport#isBeingCompiled&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
